data.description: WELCOME HOME! This full brick home, situated on a double lot has so much to offer in the Oxford School District. Inside you will find 3 bedrooms, two bathrooms, a kitchen open to the living room featuring original hardwood floors, a laundry room with a pantry, and a sunroom leading to the backyard. Outside is an entertainer's dream featuring an in ground pool, gazebo, workshop, and two bay garage perfect for someone whose hobby is restoring cars. ALL patio furniture and lawnmower to remain at no additional cost.
